Release Info:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Evil has returned! Demonic powers are manifesting themselves as a myriad
of dark creatures, fighting over the fates of imprisoned souls caught in
Purgatory. Once again, it is up to Daniel Garner, in the unenviable position
of being the Curse of Darkness and the Toy of Light, to fight his way past
hordes of demons and fiends. Questions remain..."Can he stop the powerful
creatures that stand in his way? Will he ever leave the hell of Purgatory
and be reunited with his wife Catherine?" Painkiller Hell & Damnation is
a fast-paced, thrilling modern remake of an all-action shooter Classic!
